data.description: Welcome to your lakefront oasis! Step inside to discover a freshly painted interior complemented by sleek LVP flooring on the first floor, creating a modern and inviting atmosphere. The heart of this home is the spacious kitchen, featuring a huge center island with solid surface counters. Enjoy the convenience of gas cooking while admiring the serene views of the lakefront backyard. Whether you're entertaining guests or simply relaxing with loved ones, this space is sure to impress. Just minutes over the NC/VA border, this property offers an effortless commute to area military bases, downtown Norfolk, and even the Outer Banks. Call today to schedule a private viewing!
